videos.description: Cavaliers guard Ty Jerome puts Virginia up with a deep 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Virginia jumps out early with Jerome three

videos.description: Great ball movement by the Hokies leads to a Seth Allen 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Great passing leads to Allen 3

videos.description: Virginia heads into halftime up 37-23 thanks to 13-0 run capped off by Kyle Guy's 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Guy caps off 13-0 run for Virginia with 3-pointer

videos.description: Zach LeDay gets the lay-up to fall, plus the foul as Virginia Tech starts the second half on a 20-8 run.
videos.headline: LeDay's three point play fuels Hokies second half start

videos.description: Virginia Tech pulls to within one after Justin Bibbs drives and gets the tough layup to fall.
videos.headline: Virginia Tech's Bibbs gets the transition layup, and the foul

videos.description: Ty Outlaw sends the game into OT with last second tip-in for the Hokies
videos.headline: Virginia Tech's Outlaw sends game to OT with late tip-in

videos.description: Virginia's London Perrantes gives the Cavaliers a 68-65 lead late in OT with the tough driving layup.
videos.headline: Virginia takes lead in OT thanks to Perrantes lay-in

videos.description: Tied late in OT, London Perrantes gets a bad break as the ball gets stuck on the rim. The game would head into double OT.
videos.headline: Virginia's chance to take the lead ends with ball stuck on rim

videos.description: Seth Allen knocks down game winning jumper in double overtime in upset win over Virginia.
videos.headline: Virginia Tech's Seth Allen hits game winner in upset over Virginia

videos.description: Virginia Tech's Seth Allen is thankful that his team trusted him with the ball in the final seconds of double overtime so he could help his team get the upset win over No. 12 Virginia.
videos.headline: Allen knows the importance of VT's win

videos.description: ESPN analysts Cory Alexander and Anish Shroff recap Virginia Tech's upset win over No. 12 Virginia and discuss the Hokies' tournament resume.
videos.headline: Post game breakdown: Virginia Tech upsets No. 12 Virginia in double overtime
